{"tid":1362710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「投票」地鐵不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:58:44.000Z","uid":261166,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c3e7b161ab754ffa772bb2403ed0e1d628ec00d","tid":1362710,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"純理論層面討論，地鐵不合作運動未能成功引發大規模支持，最主要係因為未有共識，即未能找到最大公因數。<br />\n<br />\n主要分歧在於以下兩派:<br />\n<br />\n1，<span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span>癱瘓地鐵，間接做成罷工效果；<br />\n2，<span style=\"color: blue;\">反對</span>阻礙返工，影響民生同搵食。<br />\n<br />\n如果想取得大多數支持，方法是中間落墨:<br />\n大家投票收集意見，你會支持以下邊一個不合作運動:<br />\n<br />\n1，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放工</span></span>時間不合作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">返工</span></span>時間不合作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果成功發起放工時間不合作，<br />\n好處如下:<br />\n1，部分公司會早放，間接罷工<br />\n2，放工攪抗爭會更多人，一呼百應<br />\n3，鐘意返工搵食就遲D先放工啦，比較唔阻人搵食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如成功放工不合作，<br />\n先再升級考慮返工不合作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5983b33374d3d8c4bfc09b53d3c4f3df342b412","tid":1362710,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"只係見咁多人要搵食而反對不合作，俾多個選擇大家，唔好以為係破窗理論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有 MTR 不合作運動 telegram 可以討論"},{"pid":"1aa268506c51d6b50af1281609c3cbec948a579d","tid":1362710,"uid":289219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:21:24.000Z","msg":"對準政權！<br />\n唔好搞到市民令民意逆轉"},{"pid":"ca1c8be98a6ddf8dc1223b4c945a33f4cc88f732","tid":1362710,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"日日小貓不合作，難有效果，<br />\n只會俾反對不合作運動的聚人氣<br />\n要就要考慮全面不合作，<br />\n先能夠達成目標。"},{"pid":"7447c3f6fcd9c33ef93e5bc13d2d703df3f91e99","tid":1362710,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"1:4 無諗過返工不合作的支持度係大過放工不合作"}]}